enableInterestToken(address,uint96,addre.details: Enables support for interest earning through a specific aToken.

params._dust: small amount of underlying tokens that cannot be paid as an interest. Accounts for possible truncation errors.
params._interestReceiver: address of the interest receiver for underlying token and associated COMP tokens.
params._minInterestPaid: min amount of underlying tokens to be paid as an interest.
params._token: address of the token contract for which to enable interest.

forceDisable(address).details: Last-resort function for returning assets to the Omnibridge contract in case of some failures in the logic. Disables this contract and transfers locked tokens back to the mediator. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._token: address of the invested token contract that should be disabled.

getModuleInterfacesVersion().details: Tells the module interface version that this contract supports.

interestAmount(address).details: Tells the current accumulated interest on the invested tokens, that can be withdrawn and payed to the interest receiver.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

invest(address,uint256).details: Invests the given amount of tokens to the AAVE protocol. Only Omnibridge contract is allowed to call this method. Converts _amount of TOKENs into aTOKENs.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

investedAmount(address).details: Tells the current amount of underlying tokens that was invested into the AAVE protocol.

isInterestSupported(address).details: Tells if interest earning is supported for the specific underlying token contract.

returns._0: true, if interest earning is supported for the given token.

lendingPool().details: Tells the address of the LendingPool contract in the Ethereum Mainnet.

payInterest(address).details: Pays collected interest for the underlying token. Anyone can call this function. Earned interest is withdrawn and transferred to the specified interest receiver account.

params._token: address of the invested token contract in which interest should be paid.

setDust(address,uint96).details: Updates dust parameter for the particular token. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._dust: new amount of underlying tokens that cannot be paid as an interest. Accounts for possible truncation errors.
params._token: address of the invested token contract.

setInterestReceiver(address,address).details: Updates address of the interest receiver. Can be any address, EOA or contract. Set to 0x00..00 to disable interest transfers. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._token: address of the invested token contract.

setMinInterestPaid(address,uint256).details: Updates min interest amount that can be transferred in single call. Only owner is allowed to call this method.

params._minInterestPaid: new amount of TOKENS and can be transferred to the interest receiver in single operation.
params._token: address of the invested token contract.

transferOwnership(address).details: Changes the owner of this contract.

withdraw(address,uint256).details: Withdraws at least the given amount of tokens from the AAVE protocol. Only Omnibridge contract is allowed to call this method. Converts aTOKENs into _amount of TOKENs.

params._amount: minimal amount of tokens to withdraw.
params._token: address of the invested token contract.
